This paper focuses on the spread of information over a social network, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of social networks (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and cybersecurity (cs.CYBER). The paper also discusses the use of web-based services and online evaluation of skills, which could fall under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper provides empirical data for modeling and designing web-based services, which could fall under the sub-category of social informatics (cs.SI).
